---
<section id="testimonios" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Subtle decorative blobs -->
  <div class="absolute -left-20 top-20 w-[30rem] h-[30rem] bg-brand-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-[20rem] h-[20rem] bg-brand-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-accent font-bold">Confianza</h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-brand-primary leading-tight">Lo que dicen los padres</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      
      <!-- Testimonio 1 -->
      <div class="bg-brand-light/50 p-10 rounded-3xl relative hover:bg-brand-light transition duration-500 border border-transparent hover:border-brand-primary/5 group">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-accent/20 absolute top-8 right-8 group-hover:text-brand-accent/40 transition-colors" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        <p class="text-brand-primary/80 italic mb-8 relative z-10 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mt-4">
          "Las sesiones con Melisa trajeron verdadera paz a nuestra casa. La forma en que conectó con nuestro hijo fue mágica desde el primer día."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary font-bold font-serif">
            M
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-sm">Mamá de J.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-brand-primary/50">Niño de 8 años</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 2 -->
      <div class="bg-brand-light/50 p-10 rounded-3xl relative hover:bg-brand-light transition duration-500 border border-transparent hover:border-brand-primary/5 group">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-accent/20 absolute top-8 right-8 group-hover:text-brand-accent/40 transition-colors" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        <p class="text-brand-primary/80 italic mb-8 relative z-10 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mt-4">
          "Nos dio herramientas súper prácticas para manejar las rabietas. Realmente sabe lo que hace, la recomendamos totalmente."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary font-bold font-serif">
            P
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-sm">Papás de L.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-brand-primary/50">Niña de 4 años</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonio 3 -->
      <div class="bg-brand-light/50 p-10 rounded-3xl relative hover:bg-brand-light transition duration-500 border border-transparent hover:border-brand-primary/5 group lg:col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-brand-accent/20 absolute top-8 right-8 group-hover:text-brand-accent/40 transition-colors" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.748-9.57 9-10.609l.996 2.151c-2.433.917-3.996 3.638-3.996 5.849h3.983v10h-9.983z"/></svg>
        <p class="text-brand-primary/80 italic mb-8 relative z-10 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mt-4">
          "Después de la detallada evaluación psicométrica, por fin entendimos cómo apoyar mejor a nuestra hija en la escuela."
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-primary font-bold font-serif">
            F
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-brand-primary text-sm">Familia R.</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-brand-primary/50">Terapia / Evaluación</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
